==English==

===Etymology===
From [[w:Adobe Photoshop|Adobe Photoshop]], a well-known and widely-used graphics editor.

===Transitive verb===
'''to photoshop''' ([[photoshops]], [[photoshopped]], [[photoshopping]])
# {{Internet}} to [[digital]]ly edit or alter a [[picture]] or [[photograph]].

==== Usage note ====
''Photoshop'' is a registered trademark of Adobe Systems, and they object to its usage as a common verb.

* http://www.adobe.com/misc/trade.html

